<Layout title="About Us — Raising Impact">

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <section class="about-intro">
<p class="intro-lead">Raising Impact acts as a strategic bridge between three pillars: <strong>intentional philanthropists</strong>, <strong>expert implementers</strong>, and the <strong>existing body of evidence</strong>. Rather than prescribing priorities, we meet the ecosystem where it is. We provide structured, context-sensitive advisory, grounded in rigorous research and sector expertise, to ensure philanthropic capital reaches its most effective destination.</p>

    <div class="mission-callout">
      <span class="mission-label">Our Mission</span>
      <p>To maximize the impact of every dollar spent.</p>
    </div>

    <p>Raising Impact undertakes rigorous cause-area research, conducts state-level and sector-level analyses, engages subject-matter experts and on-ground organisations, and applies structured processes to evaluate the cost-effectiveness and scalability of interventions. Drawing on global models such as <a href="https://www.founderspledge.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">Founders Pledge</a> and <a href="https://www.givewell.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">GiveWell</a>, Raising Impact adapts these analytical frameworks to the Indian context, intending to expand across Asia.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- OUR JOURNEY -->
  <section class="journey">
    <div class="journey-inner">
      <h2 class="journey-main-title">Our journey <em>so far.</em></h2>
      <p class="journey-intro">Three engagements. Three cause areas. A discipline of finding cost-effective philanthropy where the evidence is thinnest and the leverage is highest.</p>

      <div class="journey-cards">

        <!-- 01 -->
        <div class="journey-card">
          <div class="journey-card-left">
            <div class="journey-num-row">
              <span class="journey-num">01</span>
              <span class="journey-tag">ECCE Pilot · Maharashtra</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="journey-card-title">The richest state. The <em>thinnest</em> evidence.</h3>
            <p class="journey-card-body">Our pilot in Early Childhood Care &amp; Education exposed Maharashtra's paradox: India's wealthiest state, yet failing on key child-development indicators — and crowded out by a tiny philanthropic pool.</p>
            <div class="journey-stats">
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">$6.1M</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Total ECCE philanthropy / yr</span>
              </div>
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">#1</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Richest state, India</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="journey-card-right">
            <span class="outcome-label">Outcome</span>
            <div class="outcome-stat">18<span class="outcome-x">×</span></div>
            <p class="outcome-desc-title">Cost-effectiveness gain</p>
            <p class="outcome-desc">One extra part-time Anganwadi Worker focused on play-based early learning.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 02 -->
        <div class="journey-card">
          <div class="journey-card-left">
            <div class="journey-num-row">
              <span class="journey-num">02</span>
              <span class="journey-tag">Farmer Livelihoods · Aug '25</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="journey-card-title">Four stages. One <em>477×</em> grantee.</h3>
            <p class="journey-card-body">A strategic engagement with an independent philanthropist (Aug 2025) to lift incomes of marginal and smallholder farmers — focused on horticulture, high-value crops and allied sectors. We designed a four-stage grant call to surface mid-sized NGOs in priority states.</p>
            <div class="journey-stats">
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">4</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Stage grant call</span>
              </div>
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">Aug '25</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Engagement start</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="journey-card-right">
            <span class="outcome-label">Outcome</span>
            <div class="outcome-stat">477<span class="outcome-x">×</span></div>
            <p class="outcome-desc-title">Grantee cost-effectiveness</p>
            <p class="outcome-desc">Mid-sized NGO surfaced through our four-stage diligence process.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 03 -->
        <div class="journey-card">
          <div class="journey-card-left">
            <div class="journey-num-row">
              <span class="journey-num">03</span>
              <span class="journey-tag">Women's Empowerment · In Progress</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="journey-card-title">Defining the <em>frontier</em> before funding it.</h3>
            <p class="journey-card-body">We are in the early stages of a new engagement — partnering with an independent philanthropist to establish a definition and framework for women's empowerment, identify areas of need, and pinpoint where philanthropic capital can have maximum leverage.</p>
            <div class="journey-stats">
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">Scoping</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Philanthropic framework</span>
              </div>
              <div class="journey-stat">
                <span class="journey-stat-value">Target</span>
                <span class="journey-stat-label">Identification underway</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="journey-card-right">
            <span class="outcome-label">Outcome</span>
            <p class="outcome-stat-text">In<br/>progress</p>
            <p class="outcome-desc">Framework, scoping, and target identification underway.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW WE WORK -->
  <section class="how-we-work">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-tag">Process</div>
      <h2>How We Work</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="steps-grid">
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">01</div>
        <h4>Cause Area Research</h4>
        <p>State and sector analyses to target high-impact philanthropy.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">02</div>
        <h4>Expert Engagement</h4>
        <p>Experts and field partners validate research, implementation fidelity and feasibility.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">03</div>
        <h4>Structured Evaluation</h4>
        <p>Cost-effectiveness analysis using adapted <a href="https://www.givewell.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">GiveWell</a> and <a href="https://www.founderspledge.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-link">Founders Pledge</a> methods.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="step-card">
        <div class="step-num">04</div>
        <h4>Capital Deployment</h4>
        <p>Donors matched with vetted, deployment-ready organisations.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHY PARTNER -->
  <section class="why-partner">
    <div class="why-partner-inner">
      <h2>Why Partner With Us</h2>
      <div class="gold-bar-sm"></div>
      <table class="partner-table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Feature</th>
            <th>Benefit</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>Vetted Pipeline</td>
            <td>Pre-screened, high-fidelity organizations ready for capital</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Shared Expertise</td>
            <td>Benefit from the collective intelligence of founding partners</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Measurable RoI</td>
            <td>Confidence that your capital is linked to data-backed, scalable outcomes</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Deep Partnership</td>
            <td>A trusted extension of your personal philanthropic vision</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TEAM -->
  <section class="team">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-tag">People</div>
      <h2>Our Team</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="team-intro">
      <p>The RIO team brings together decades of experience across Indian philanthropy, public policy, nonprofit operations, and sector research. We combine:</p>
      <div class="team-traits">
        <span class="trait-pill">Analytical depth</span>
        <span class="trait-pill">Ecosystem network</span>
        <span class="trait-pill">Strong regional insight</span>
        <span class="trait-pill">Evidence-driven outcomes</span>
      </div>
      <p>Collaboration is at the heart of our work — whether with philanthropists, NGOs, state governments, or peer research organisations.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 36px;">
      <div class="section-tag">Founding Team</div>
    </div>

    <div class="team-grid">
      {team.map((member) => (
        <div class="team-card">
          <div class="team-avatar-wrap">
            <img src={member.img} alt={member.name} class="team-avatar-img" />
          </div>
          <div class="team-card-info">
            <h4 class="team-name">{member.name}</h4>
            <p class="team-role">{member.role}</p>
            <a href={member.linkedin} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="team-linkedin">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M19 0H5C2.239 0 0 2.239 0 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5V5c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zM8 19H5V8h3v11zM6.5 6.732c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zM20 19h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0V19h-3V8h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476V19z"/>
              </svg>
              LinkedIn
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
